column5: Fishing for carp has been really good this season! Many fish landed but here is a shot of the BEST outing of 2015 (to date) with my eldest son and youngest daughter.
Nice man! Family fishing at its finest!
Right on man! Nice fat carp too
Yes, very nice carp and bonus family memories. Thanks for sharing.
Nice fatty there Jimmy.  And great that you're able to bring your whole dang gag with ya!  lol
